article.description: — KJ Jenkins had 20 points in UNC Wilmington's 78-69 victory against College of Charleston on Saturday night.
article.headline: Jenkins scores 20 as UNC Wilmington takes down College of Charleston 78-69
article.linkText: Jenkins scores 20 as UNC Wilmington takes down College of Charleston 78-69
article.story: WILMINGTON, N.C. -- — KJ Jenkins had 20 points in UNC Wilmington's 78-69 victory against College of Charleston on Saturday night. Jenkins was 7 of 13 shooting, including 3 for 7 from 3-point range, and went 3 for 3 from the line for the Seahawks (13-5, 4-2 Coastal Athletic Association). Shykeim Phillips scored 18 points and added six assists and three steals. Trazarien White shot 6 for 16 (1 for 3 from 3-point range) and 4 of 6 from the free throw line to finish with 17 points. The Cougars (13-6, 4-2) were led by Ante Brzovic, who recorded 27 points and 11 rebounds. Jordan Crawford added 12 points for Charleston. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
